    "body": "## Problem\r\nCan't easily show an animated \"spinner\" in statusline.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nAdds API for setting up, starting and stopping an animated spinner.\r\nLargely based on https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/34562#issuecomment-2991242967\r\n\r\ncloses #34562\r\n\r\n\r\n### todo\r\n- [ ] add tests\r\n- [ ] finish up docs",
    "closed_at": "2025-06-23T10:39:27Z",
