            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "After sleeping on this, I don't think `char` is the best name here. In theory, there is nothing wrong with showing spinner with more than a single character. For example, like [this one](https://github.com/sindresorhus/cli-spinners/blob/a01e4cf1235e1425f0243f36887db168cf710279/spinners.json#L656).\r\n\r\nNot sure about the appropriate name here, though. Can be `str` for \"string\". Can also be `frame`, as used in 'sindresorhus/cli-spinners'.",
            "commit_id": "a31e43d42c1603787c4b54c8d290eba41f7804a6",
            "created_at": "2025-06-22T07:35:52Z",
